<template>
    <v-btn class="filter-button" :class="{ toggled: isToggled }" @click="isToggled = !isToggled">
        <slot></slot>
    </v-btn>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    data: function () {
        return {
            isToggled: false
        }
    }
}
</script>
